    "Beyond that, LLM-based evaluation of scientific data and publications may only be one of several options for AI assistance in literature analysis.",
    "Future systems may combine different ML and AI approaches for optimal automated processing of literature and scientific data.",
    "Limitations of LLM-based title and abstract screeningEven though the LLM-based screening presented in our work shows some promising results, it also has some drawbacks and limitations.",
